title: Ep 2283 - Gokuldham Gears Up For Ganeshutsav
shortDesc: Tappu Sena meet at Bhide's house to discuss the arrangements for the Ganesh festival. Bhide is anxious to know what Tappu Sena has planned for the festival. However, they refuse to divulge any details.

title: Ep 2284 - A Traditional Celebration At Gokuldham
shortDesc: The residents of Gokuldham dress up traditionally and welcome Lord Ganesha on their premises with much fanfare. All the residents perform the 'aarti'. Later, Tappu Sena reveal that the residents must participate in a fancy dress competition.

title: Ep 2285 - Jethalal Goes Missing
shortDesc: While everyone is gearing up to perform at the fancy dress competition, Jethalal is unable to decide what he will perform. Just before the function, he goes missing. All the residents of Gokuldham are surprised by his absence.

title: Ep 2286 - Jethalals Absence Creates Panic
shortDesc: Popatlal informs the rest that Jethalal has not decided on his costume and was looking confused when he last met him. Subsequently, Iyer demands that Jethalal must be asked to pay one lakh rupees fine if he does not show up for the programme.

title: Ep 2288 - Jethalals Worries Continue
shortDesc: While the residents of Gokuldham continue to showcase their talent by donning different attires for the fancy dress competition, there is still speculation about Jethalal's participation and his costume.

title: Ep 2289 - And The Winner Is...
shortDesc: The fancy dress contest at Gokuldham Society reaches its last leg. When Jethalal's turn comes to perform, he stuns everyone by portraying himself as a common man and addressing common man's problems.

title: Ep 2290 - The Boring Breakfast
shortDesc: Jethalal is eager to have a sumptuous breakfast. However, he is upset when he finds that Daya has prepared a snack, which is different from the regular fare, and refuses to eat. At the same time, Babita gets the same dish prepared from her place.

title: Ep 2291 - Dayas Love For Jethalal
shortDesc: Jethalal and Mr Mehta head to a hotel nearby, but they are disappointed when they do not find anything worthwhile there. At the office, Jethalal is surprised when Tappu gets food packed for him and praises Daya for showering him with love.

title: Ep 2292 - Gokuldhams Notice Board Goes Missing
shortDesc: Atmaram Bhide is unable to decide on the 'Thought For The Day' to be written on Gokuldham society's notice board. As he makes way to write, he is shocked to find the board missing.

title: Ep 2293 - Chalu Pandey Returns
shortDesc: Bhide decides to call the police to find the missing notice board. Inspector Chalu Pandey takes the case in his hands. Suddenly, everyone is surprised to know that Tappu sena took the notice board.

title: Ep 2294 - Tapus New Smartwatch
shortDesc: Tapu shows his new smartwatch to Tapu sena. Sonu tells that Goli strictly needs this smartwatch to manage his weight. Then, Bhide scolds Tapu for buying such an expensive watch.

title: Ep 2295 - Professor Bhide Becomes A Shopkeeper
shortDesc: Abdul asks Bhide to look after his shop until he returns after delivering cold drinks for the kitty party. Bhide faces a problem when a customer asks him for a pen, and he is unable to tell its price.

title: Ep 2296 - The Spiked Drink
shortDesc: The society members call the salespersons to their clubhouse to show the demo. They present their demo in an interesting way to keep the society members entertained.

title: Ep 2297 - The Smart Chase
shortDesc: After Tappu Sena find most of the Golhuldham residents in an unconscious state at the clubhouse, they make desperate efforts to wake them up. They decide to catch the two salesmen, but are forced to let them go when Gogi is held at gunpoint.

title: Ep 2298 - Chai
shortDesc: Tapu sena and Abdul follow Chai-Patti gang and catch them. Meanwhile, Chalu Pandey arrives at the spot and arrests them. Tapu Sena returns to the Gokuldham society delighted.
